<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description>龙龙的技术博客</description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2017 17:09:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>夜饮微醺</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-yin-wei-xun/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;此心憔悴不思量，望家长盼浣纱娘。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;只言片语空度日，木架犹悬嫁衣裳。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>我的诗词</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-yin-wei-xun/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2017 17:06:44 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>夜酌听诗</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-zhuo-ting-shi/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;小楼独酌诗酒茶，当年何处后庭花。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;孤星暗月空自许，秋千院落夜还家。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>我的诗词</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-zhuo-ting-shi/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2017 14:27:31 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题21——利用圆的切线作直角</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-21-li-yong-yuan-de-qie-xian-zuo-zhi-jiao/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p21-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p21-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题不算难，条件很丰富，方法也很多，在这里我们用圆的切线来作图。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、画已知部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p21-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p21-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、作切线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p21-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p21-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、连接圆心和切点。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p21-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p21-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p21-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p21-4.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-21-li-yong-yuan-de-qie-xian-zuo-zhi-jiao/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2017 13:19:55 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题20——画指定角度和长度的弦2</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-20-hua-zhi-ding-jiao-du-he-chang-du-de-xian-2/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-7.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题和 &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-19-hua-zhi-ding-jiao-du-he-chang-du-de-xian-1/"&gt;https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-19-hua-zhi-ding-jiao-du-he-chang-du-de-xian-1/&lt;/a&gt; 是一样的道理，就不用多解释了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p20-7.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-20-hua-zhi-ding-jiao-du-he-chang-du-de-xian-2/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2017 13:10:50 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题19——画指定角度和长度的弦1</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-19-hua-zhi-ding-jiao-du-he-chang-du-de-xian-1/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这个题算是 &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-6-yi-zhi-yuan-xin-suo-zai-zhi-xian-he-yi-tiao-xian-chang-hua-yuan-hua-zhi-ding-jiao-du-he-chang-du-de-xian/"&gt;https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-6-yi-zhi-yuan-xin-suo-zai-zhi-xian-he-yi-tiao-xian-chang-hua-yuan-hua-zhi-ding-jiao-du-he-chang-du-de-xian/&lt;/a&gt; 的精简版，只需要画指定角度和长度的弦。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画已知的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、利用偏移画固定长度的弦。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、加上固定角度。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、旋转。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p19-6.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-19-hua-zhi-ding-jiao-du-he-chang-du-de-xian-1/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2017 12:56:02 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题18——利用固定角度三角形画不规则多边形</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-18-li-yong-gu-ding-jiao-du-san-jiao-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题不大好用平行四边形了，因为75度下边对应的两个角的度数目前都不知道，这就导致没法作目标直线的平行线。所以我们不妨换个思路。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画已知部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、连接两个端点，构成三角形，这时，我们发现上边要画的部分就是固定顶角三角形，这时就好下手了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p18-6.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-18-li-yong-gu-ding-jiao-du-san-jiao-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2017 12:10:11 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题17——利用平行四边形画不规则多边形5</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-17-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-5/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题看上去不大容易直接构造平行四边形了，那又该用什么黑科技呢？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画已知部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、还是和之前 &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-13-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-1/"&gt;https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-13-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-1/&lt;/a&gt; 相似的方法，构造一条和目标直线平行且相等的线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、问题是怎么把上一步的直线平移到两个圆上，并且还两端都各自正好搭到一个圆呢？下面看看黑科技。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p17-6.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-17-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-5/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2017 11:33:53 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题16——利用平行四边形画不规则多边形4</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-16-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-4/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p16-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p16-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题的方法与 &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-13-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-1/"&gt;https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-13-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-1/&lt;/a&gt; 也是一致的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先分别画已知的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p16-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p16-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、构造平行四边形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p16-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p16-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p16-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p16-3.PNG"&gt;
