&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题的方法与 &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-13-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-1/"&gt;https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-13-li-yong-ping-xing-si-bian-xing-hua-bu-gui-ze-duo-bian-xing-1/&lt;/a&gt; 也是一致的，只是多了一个平移，当然这里的做法不止这一种。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先分别画已知的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p15-1.PNG"&gt;
